=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104iej1741086838875.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iej1741086838875.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/iej1741086838875.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"iej1741086838875\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Specify if function $length returns the length in bytes or characters for arguments with\n\t\tdatatype Raw.</p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iej1741086838875__section_w1399ab1b5b1_w1400ab1b5_w1401ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">$LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES{=} 1 | 0</code></p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iej1741086838875__section_z2l_h4h_42c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d974089e56\"><strong class=\"ph b\">Defaults</strong></h2>\n<div class=\"p\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table frame-all\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"iej1741086838875__table_emk_q4h_42c\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\"></span></caption><colgroup><col style=\"width:50%\"/><col style=\"width:50%\"/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Assignment file:</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Any application assignment file</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Section:</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">[SETTINGS]</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\">\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">Default value:</td>\n<td class=\"entry colsep-1 rowsep-1\">0 </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"iej1741086838875__section_pm2_z4h_42c\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d974089e108\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\">Use <code class=\"ph codeph\">$LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES</code> to differentiate between the byte length\n\t\t\t\tand character length for raw data when using <code class=\"ph codeph\">$length</code>.</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"iej1741086838875__ul_t3y_bph_42c\">\n<li class=\"li\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">$LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 0</code> or is omitted, $length returns the\n\t\t\t\t\tcharacter length for raw data.</li>\n<li class=\"li\">If <code class=\"ph codeph\">$LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 1</code>, $length returns the byte length\n\t\t\t\t\tfor raw data.</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_12316097\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_12316097\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated März 05, 2025 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Specify if function $length returns the length in bytes or characters for arguments with datatype Raw. $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES{=} 1 | 0 Defaults Table 1. Assignment file: Any application assignment file Section: [SETTINGS] Default value: 0 Description Use $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES to differentiate between the byte length and character length for raw data when using $length . If $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 0 or is omitted, $length returns the character length for raw data. If $LENGTH_RAW_IN_BYTES = 1 , $length returns the byte length for raw data. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}